  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Second Life Supplies for Elders in South America</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Afya Foundation has strong linkages with many communities across the globe in dire need of medical supplies for its aging residents. The materials donated, after a loved one has passed away or recovered from an accident,  can give a second life to these supplies to improve the quality of life for the elderly poor abroad while preventing the devastating environmental impact of simply discarding them.  Help us donate hundreds of wheelchairs, walkers, commodes and more to change and save lives.</narrative>
  </description>
